These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-1::.
House: palace, townhouse, tower, art-deco
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, poppy, orchid
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, d&b, dubstep, pop
1. the fan dubstep is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the fan pop is the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the tower house is on the far left##1
4. the palace house is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the fan dubstep and the townhouse house##2
6. the fan d&b is the person who growspoppy##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| House        | tower | art-deco  | townhouse | palace  |
| Flower         | orchid    | balloon-flower  | begonia       | poppy     |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | reggae | pop       | d&b |

