.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, water, juice
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, folk, ambient, salsa
4 different games are played: snooker, billiard, monopoly, whist
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
2. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person playing billiard is on the far left##1
4. the person playing whist is between the fan salsa and the person drinking juice##2
5. the fan salsa is the person playing billiard##1
6. the fan blues is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
7. the fan ambient is the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4       |
| Beverage         | 7up | hot-chocolate    | juice  | water |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | blues  | folk   | ambient    |
| Game         | billiard | whist | snooker | monopoly      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, marigold, lily, bellflower
House: colonial, tower, farmhouse, futuristic
There are 4 different nationalities: british, canadian, polish, turkish
1. the canadian is between the turkish and the person who growsmarigold##2
2. the colonial house is on the left of the british##1
3. the tower house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the person who growslily is on the far right##1
5. the tower house is on the far left##1
6. the british is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1
7. the polish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Flower      | marigold | bellflower         | daffodil   | lily    |
| House         | tower | futuristic | colonial | farmhouse |
| Nationality   | polish   | canadian        | turkish      | british   |

