There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, red, pink
4 different games are played: backgammon, domino, scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing scrabble is on the far left##1
2. the person playing backgammon is between the person playing billiard and the fan metal##2
3. the fan folk is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who likes red##1
5. the fan folk is on the right of the fan electronic##1
6. the person playing billiard is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person playing domino##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | metal        | soul   | electronic | folk |
| Color         | red | aquamarine | lilac    | pink |
| Game     | scrabble       | backgammon     | billiard       | domino    |

