.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, marigold, poppy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, october, june
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, action, horror, crime
1. the person watching crime movies is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsbegonia##2
2. the person watching crime movies is the person who growspoppy##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
7. the person watching crime movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person who's birthday is in february##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |      3      |     4      |
| Flower   | daisy | poppy      | begonia       | marigold   |
| Birthday      | february   | may  | june | october     |
| Movie-Genre      | action     | crime | horror        | satire |

