.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, begonia, tulip, marigold
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, doctor, firefighter, freelancer
City: boston, liverpool, miami, hannover
1. the freelancer is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the librarian is between the freelancer and the person traveling to miami##2
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who growsorchid and the person who growstulip##2
7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the firefighter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Flower    | tulip | begonia  | orchid | marigold      |
| Job   | firefighter  | freelancer  | librarian | doctor |
| City   | hannover | boston | liverpool | miami     |

