.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, magic-tricks, collecting, cooking
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rat, mouse, cat
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, coffee, almond-milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is the owner of the rat##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the mouse##2
7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby          | collecting  | magic-tricks    | cooking | gardening  |
| Pet   | mouse | cat       | rat        | hamster    |
| Beverage         | coffee | lemonade | 7up  | almond-milk |

