4. the cape-cod house is the person who likes turquise##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes lilac##1
6. the cape-cod house is on the far right##1
7. the ranch-style house is between the bolivar-smoker and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
