4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is the prince-smoker##1
8. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage          | cola      | juice | tea | hot-chocolate |
