.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
House: modern, farmhouse, craftsman, cottage
City: london, boston, miami, venice
4 different games are played: domino, poker, chess, mah-jongg
1. the farmhouse house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the person playing chess is the farmhouse house##1
3. the person playing domino is between the person traveling to boston and the person traveling to miami##2
4. the person traveling to miami is between the person playing domino and the cottage house##2
5. the person traveling to miami is the person playing mah-jongg##1
6. the person traveling to london is the person playing poker##1
7. the person traveling to venice is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
