3. the baccarat-smoker is between the aristoff-smoker and the person who likes ebony##2
4. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
5. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
7. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
