The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, april, january
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, dannemann, siglo, bluemaster
1. the person who likes lavender is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who likes blood-red##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the far left##1
5. the dannemann-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who likes light-blue##2
6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
7. the fonseca-smoker is between the bluemaster-smoker and the dannemann-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
