.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, april, march, november
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, lemon, corn, watermelon
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon, whist, canasta
1. the person eating strawberry is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person playing backgammon##2
3. the person who's birthday is in march is the person eating lemon##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person eating corn and the person playing canasta##2
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the person playing mah-jongg is between the person playing whist and the person eating watermelon##2
7. the person eating strawberry is the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday      | april | march | august   | november |
| Food   | strawberry  | lemon    | corn   | watermelon     |
| Game   | canasta  | whist | mah-jongg | backgammon   |

