4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, blend, swisher, montecristo
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, february, january
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
2. the swisher-smoker is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's birthday is in february##2
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
5. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the blend-smoker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Hobby   | woodworking    | photography | fishing           | board-games |
| Cigar       | cain | swisher    | blend          | montecristo   |
| Birthday      | february  | march   | january | june  |

