3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person playing chess is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes aquamarine##2
5. the security-guard is on the left of the person playing poker##1
6. the project-manager is between the person playing canasta and the doctor##2
7. the person who likes blood-red is the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Game      | billiard | chess | canasta     | poker   |
| Color   | aquamarine | blood-red        | fuchsia  | lilac  |
| Job           | doctor      | project-manager         | security-guard | writer |

